lead_paragraph: The success of Iceland, who face hosts France in the quarter-finals of Euro 2016 on Sunday, shocked some people but, for Nigerian midfielder Dickson Etuhu who has worked with their Swedish joint coach Lars Lagerback, it comes as no surprise.

headline.print_headline: Lagerback's Composure and Planning Are Iceland's Secret
headline.main: Lagerback's Composure and Planning Are Iceland's Secret
